Module takMashido.shani
Package takMashido.shani

Class Engine

java.lang.Object
takMashido.shani.Engine
public class Engine
extends java.lang.Object
Main class of shani. Responsible for all data loading and intends flow. For service functions it contains only core of implementation, all helper code and methods with different args are in ShaniCore class.
Author:
TakMashido

      public static Intend getIntend() throws java.lang.InterruptedException
      Get filtered intend. It's blocking method, if no intend available wait's until it comes.
      Returns:
      The oldest registered intend.
      Throws:
      java.lang.InterruptedException - If thread is interrupted during waiting for new Intend.

    • isInputPositive

      public static java.lang.Boolean isInputPositive​(ShaniString input)
      Checks if input is positive response. Return true for positive/agreeding one (yes,youp), false for negative/unagriding (no,nope), or false for unrecognized one. Actual positive/negative pattern depends on value stored in config file(TODO move to mainFile)
      Parameters:
      input - ShaniString to check if is positive response.
      Returns:
      If given input indicates positive response (return true), negative (returns false) or is unknown(null).
